Black Girl (1966)  ni [[Senegali|Filime yo muri Senegali]] yanditswe numwanditsi / umuyobozi Ousmane Sembène, yakinnye na Mbissine Thérèse Diop <ref>https://www.criterion.com/films/28849-black-girl</ref>. Umutwe wayo '''''wigifaransa ni La noire de…''''', bisobanura ngo "Umukobwa / umugore wumwirabura wa…",<ref>https://www.criterion.com/current/posts/4402-black-girl-self-possessed</ref> , cyangwa " Iyi filime yibanze kuri Diouana, umukobwa ukiri muto wo muri Senegali, wimukiye i Dakar, muri Senegali yerekeza muri Antibes<ref>https://www.newyorker.com/goings-on-about-town/movies/black-girl-2</ref>, mu Bufaransa gukorera umugabo n'umugore b'Abafaransa. Mu Bufaransa, Diouana yizeye gukomeza akazi yakoraga nk'umubyaza<ref>https://www.criterionchannel.com/black-girl</ref>, kandi ateganya ubuzima bushya bw'isi. Ariko, ageze muri Antibes, Diouana ahura n’umugabo n'umugore, bamuhatira gukora nk'umukozi<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/black-girl--borom-sarret-1969</ref>. Agenda arushaho kumenya imiterere ye ko itandukanye atangira kwibaza ubuzima bwe mubufaransa<ref>https://uchv.princeton.edu/events/black-girl-1966-ousmane-sembene</ref>.   Bikunze gufatwa nka firime ya mbere yo munsi yubutayu bwa Sahara numukinnyi wamafirime nyafurika yitabiriwe n’amahanga.Inkuru ishingiye kubintu byabayeho<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/may/18/black-girl-review-ousmene-sembene-groundbreaking</ref>.
